The paper deals with the task of automatically identifying data types of web structured data, which is a problem related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed approach uses deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed strategy in different web domains, which is related to database systems (cs.DB).
